  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5411437908f600182c7935d72b1fd31e.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5411437908f600182c7935d72b1fd31e.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/346e536953541b20154061e07c3cd622.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br>The world has come to an end.<br>All civilizations disappeared, and the empty places seem to be occupied by the monsters.<br><br>Led by their last lingering feelings of the extinct world, the few survivors each happen to gather in a castle built on a fief.  <br><br>They were born into different races, have lived in different places, and have different purposes.<br>Now they have to work together to achieve their own specific goals.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/12e1f3c70d08f5f123f31cd653f721ec.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/12e1f3c70d08f5f123f31cd653f721ec.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/3abdd01055c8e4557242ffffdd2da880.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=324 /></span><br><br>Each character has different stories and different skill sets.<br>Some parry off or avoid enemy attacks, but some fight recklessly, ignoring their damage.<br><br>Face your reckless enemies with every four characters with a different style of play.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/f2f2cb3173fa803786f8dc6a5db00215.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/f2f2cb3173fa803786f8dc6a5db00215.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/e14864819abdae839dad0707dea85741.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=298 /></span><br><br>You can choose and use each character's skills.<br>Each skill can be strengthened in different ways through Glyphs and increase performance when you level up with each character. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.mp4?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And can overcome the moment of crisis with scrolls and strengthen yourself through relics.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/74fa13d7d9822d7c333314f167504b65.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/74fa13d7d9822d7c333314f167504b65.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/7ab574723b1a4f143a73d7c27bfab34d.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=168 /></span><br><br>If you lose a battle, you lose progress and return to your hideout, but that doesn't mean a complete reset.<br><br>You can unlock permanent reinforcement in hiding places, discover new artifacts, or find ways to speed up your next exploration.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5e6cdb8aeb2c42c900e7e0f94d67119e.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5e6cdb8aeb2c42c900e7e0f94d67119e.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/d27de5e98f5088aa6c697603f0dcaf88.avif?t=1725942268\" width=650 height=286 /></span><br><br>The environment and enemies encountered in each expedition may vary, but the castle structure is fixed.<br>You may also be able to find a new path in the castle.<br><br>And you will have to choose your move of direction every time you encounter the next node.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5220524afbdeb41cce56ce7893ac975a.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5220524afbdeb41cce56ce7893ac975a.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A skill-based roguelike (rogue-lite) action game with 4 main characters.<br></li><li> Cinematic videos where each character's story exists.<br></li><li> Powerful bosses, randomly combined champions, dozens of monsters.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5411437908f600182c7935d72b1fd31e.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5411437908f600182c7935d72b1fd31e.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/346e536953541b20154061e07c3cd622.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br>The world has come to an end.<br>All civilizations disappeared, and the empty places seem to be occupied by the monsters.<br><br>Led by their last lingering feelings of the extinct world, the few survivors each happen to gather in a castle built on a fief.  <br><br>They were born into different races, have lived in different places, and have different purposes.<br>Now they have to work together to achieve their own specific goals.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/12e1f3c70d08f5f123f31cd653f721ec.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/12e1f3c70d08f5f123f31cd653f721ec.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/3abdd01055c8e4557242ffffdd2da880.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=324 /></span><br><br>Each character has different stories and different skill sets.<br>Some parry off or avoid enemy attacks, but some fight recklessly, ignoring their damage.<br><br>Face your reckless enemies with every four characters with a different style of play.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/f2f2cb3173fa803786f8dc6a5db00215.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/f2f2cb3173fa803786f8dc6a5db00215.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/e14864819abdae839dad0707dea85741.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=298 /></span><br><br>You can choose and use each character's skills.<br>Each skill can be strengthened in different ways through Glyphs and increase performance when you level up with each character. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/b2dfad503761a8be6183b71c90d32b75.mp4?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And can overcome the moment of crisis with scrolls and strengthen yourself through relics.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/74fa13d7d9822d7c333314f167504b65.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/74fa13d7d9822d7c333314f167504b65.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/7ab574723b1a4f143a73d7c27bfab34d.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=168 /></span><br><br>If you lose a battle, you lose progress and return to your hideout, but that doesn't mean a complete reset.<br><br>You can unlock permanent reinforcement in hiding places, discover new artifacts, or find ways to speed up your next exploration.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5e6cdb8aeb2c42c900e7e0f94d67119e.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5e6cdb8aeb2c42c900e7e0f94d67119e.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/d27de5e98f5088aa6c697603f0dcaf88.avif?t=1725942268\" width=650 height=286 /></span><br><br>The environment and enemies encountered in each expedition may vary, but the castle structure is fixed.<br>You may also be able to find a new path in the castle.<br><br>And you will have to choose your move of direction every time you encounter the next node.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5220524afbdeb41cce56ce7893ac975a.poster.avif?t=1725942268\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935100/extras/5220524afbdeb41cce56ce7893ac975a.webm?t=1725942268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A skill-based roguelike (rogue-lite) action game with 4 main characters.<br></li><li> Cinematic videos where each character's story exists.<br></li><li> Powerful bosses, randomly combined champions, dozens of monsters.</li></ul>",
